# CODEOWNERS
# This file specifies individuals or teams that own certain patterns of code in the repository.
# When someone opens a pull request that modifies code owned by a CODEOWNERS entry,
# those code owners are automatically requested as reviewers.

# Format: <file-pattern>    <@username_or_team>

# Example Owners:
# Global owner for all code
# * @your-github-username

# Docs folder owner
# docs/ @your-docs-team

# Hot path modules (requires special attention)
# modules/sim-kernel/ @performance-engineers
# modules/runtime/     @performance-engineers

# Specific feature owners
# modules/features/tech/ @tech-team
# modules/features/magic/ @magic-developers

# Build logic owner
# build-logic/ @gradle-experts
